Class CardMergeInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport.CardMergeInfo

  • public final class CardMergeInfo
extends Object
    The identifier of an original Card in its host Item, together with the identifier of the copied Card that was created during a merge operation.
